{"tid":1011565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女店員遇匪想落跑　竟被肥婆同事抓回當肉盾挨刀","createTime":"2019-02-07T01:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T01:48:31.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dc17d07d23c0858bab93da90f613469d82e9cb80","tid":1011565,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"見證人性！泰國那空叻差是瑪府一間便利店上月底遭到一名搶匪持刀搶劫，在搶匪要闖入櫃檯時，原本一名女店員要翻越櫃檯逃跑，結果卻被同事抓回來充當自己的肉盾，結果腹部被刺傷縫了6針。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國《Post Today》網站報導，事發在1月29日，當時一名戴著口罩的黑衣男進入便利店後拿出刀子威脅女店員將錢交出，隨即便要闖進櫃檯，女店員急忙想要翻越櫃檯逃跑，結果卻被女同事攬腰抱回櫃檯裡，而且女同事還用雙手緊緊將想離開的女店員扣在自己身體前方，結果搶匪進櫃檯後舉刀就刺，被抓回來的女店員成了同事的肉盾。<br />\n這名搶劫在2月2日被警方逮捕，他供稱是自己沒錢、沒工作，但要買新的摩托車，所以才拿持刀行搶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20190207/1513712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20190207%2F1513712&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYBn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=10950a9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20190207%2F1513712&h=289545dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20190207/1513712</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190207/640_be88e2ff9925d0cbbd48a046aa48e179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190207%2F640_be88e2ff9925d0cbbd48a046aa48e179.jpg&h=bfc1ecf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去看片，好賤"},{"pid":"7b03837d96a344c40e75390d972342f5f58e98d4","tid":1011565,"uid":179979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T01:19:14.000Z","msg":"真係好撚仆街wo<br />\n會唔會係夾埋"},{"pid":"c4affff191a9963bd2c6e9a7c62d56fa80f2367b","tid":1011565,"uid":46587,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"肥婆冇好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcbb0258406bf86dbcd49b1095000a79dd59a72","tid":1011565,"u